### Get single
GET http://{{host}}/api/vehicles/{{VehicleID}}

### Modify
PUT http://{{host}}/api/vehicles/{{VehicleID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "type":"Van",
    "make":"Tesla",
    "model":"3"
}

### Delete (won't work without query string "login=johndoe")
DELETE http://{{host}}/api/vehicles/{{VehicleID}}

### Delete with user information
DELETE http://{{host}}/api/vehicles/{{VehicleID}}?login=johndoe
